videos.headline: Book coughs up ball
videos.description: Ian Book loses control of the ball on his way down, and upon review, Clemson wins the challenge and turns the Irish over on their second possession.

videos.headline: Eagle runs amok at Cotton Bowl pregame
videos.description: An eagle flew into the stands and landed on a fan's shoulder during the pregame festivities at the Goodyear Cotton Bowl Classic.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF highlight (Eagle runs amok at Cotton Bowl pregame) 2018/12/29

videos.headline: Tigers avoid turnover by smallest of margins
videos.description: Clemson's Derion Kendrick fumbles on a kick return, but the ball touches out of bounds by inches as Clemson retains possession.

videos.headline: Lawrence on the money to Ross for long TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence lofts a ball downfield to Justyn Ross, whose extra effort and extension results in a 52-yard Clemson touchdown.

videos.headline: Notre Dame's key sack leads to Clemson missed FG
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence gets taken down by Adetokunbo Ogundeji for a loss of 7, and Greg Huegel proceeds to miss the 49-yard field goal.

videos.headline: Lawrence threads needle to Ross for 2nd TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fires a strike to Justyn Ross in stride for a 42-yard touchdown, their second long scoring connection of the half.

videos.headline: Lawrence cracked by Tillery after pass
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence flings a 32-yard completion to Hunter Renfrow and gets laid out by Jerry Tillery, who is flagged on the late hit.

videos.headline: Clemson's Ross erupts for 2 TDs & 100+ yards in 1st half
videos.description: Justyn Ross racks up 137 receiving yards and two touchdowns in the first half of the Cotton Bowl as Clemson leads Notre Dame.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson's Ross erupts for 2 TDs & 100+ yards in 1st half) 2018/12/29 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Film Room shows how Clemson delivered long TD pass
videos.description: Mack Brown, Dave Clawson, Paul Johnson and Mike Norvell break down Trevor Lawrence's 42-yard touchdown to Justyn Ross.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF analysis (Film Room shows how Clemson delivered long TD pass) 2018/12/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelly: No one to blame but ourselves
videos.description: Brian Kelly thinks his team is making too many mistakes and has confidence they can come back in the second half.

videos.headline: Dabo on Clemson gameplan: We won't abandon run
videos.description: Dabo Swinney tells Holly Rowe that Clemson has things to clean up in the second half despite hitting on big plays in the first half.

videos.headline: Clemson uses big plays to build halftime lead
videos.description: The Clemson Tigers take a 23-3 lead into halftime against Notre Dame thanks to Trevor Lawrence's 3 TD passes and Justyn Ross' 137 yards and two scores.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson uses big plays to build halftime lead) 2018/12/29 ESHEET SotFull

videos.headline: Higgins makes spectacular one-handed TD catch
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence finds Tee Higgins, who makes a spectacular one-handed, bobbling catch for a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Higgins makes spectacular one-handed TD catch) 2018/12/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Book's shot downfield is picked off by Turner
videos.description: Ian Book's pass attempt on 3rd-and-22 is intercepted by Clemson DB Nolan Turner for Book's second turnover of the game.

videos.headline: Etienne takes off for 62-yard TD
videos.description: Travis Etienne bursts through the hole and goes the distance for the long 62-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Dabo showered in Gatorade at midfield
videos.description: Isaiah Simmons and Christian Wilkins chug to midfield and bathe Dabo Swinney in Clemson-orange Gatorade as the Tigers take down Notre Dame 30-3.

videos.headline: Dabo: We're going to celebrate this win
videos.description: Dabo Swinney talk about his team's win saying his team played well especially his quarterback, Trevor Lawrence.

videos.headline: Lawrence: Big plays gave us momentum
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence speaks about the game, saying he thought the big plays helped Clemson gain momentum and carry them to victory.

videos.headline: Wilkins credits senior leadership for Goodyear Cotton Bowl win
videos.description: Clemson's Christian Wilkins commends his fellow senior leaders for setting the standard in the locker room and on the field all season.

videos.headline: Blackledge: Not much of a gap between Clemson and Alabama
videos.description: Todd Blackledge was impressed with Clemson, saying he thinks there isn't much of a difference between Alabama and the Tigers.

videos.headline: Kelly: There was no overwhelming difference in talent
videos.description: Brian Kelly says his Notre Dame team had self-inflicting issues in their blowout loss vs. Clemson.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Kelly: There was no overwhelming difference in talent) 2018/12/29
